textString: Tokuma Shoten, Japan Airlines, Nippon Network Studio Ghibli (C) 1992 PORCO ROSSO (Italian Tenor On Radio) Yeah?
We've got a job for you!
The Mamma Aiutos gang is on the move.
We need you to protect one of our ships carring a fortune in Gold.
There's a group of school girls on board too.
See here Bouty Hunter, no fight gauging!
We've got a contract with you!
Stop the ship.Or we sink it!
Someday I'm get off my lazy butt and give this thing an overhaul.
Cmon kids we're in a hurry.
Boss do we have to take all 15 of 'em?
Yeah it's not nice to seperate them from their friends!
The Mama Auito gang has taken the girls and the gold!
I know what I'm doin' That Mama Aiuto gang is so cheap,they'll fly just of out sight and hide on the nearest island.
Just to save money on gasoline.
Don't give out on me now!
I better get this job done quick!
They know better than to be out here!
You get yourselves kidnapped by these guys, sweethearts!
I told you, we shouldn't have taken them.
Just don't let the boss know.
Let's get this thing over with.
Don't just sit there,shoot em' Shoot em' You keep missing him.
I think he's better than you!
I'll get him this time Where?
No That's not good We're sinking.
We all belong to a swimming club.
“He says - Hand over the Girls and the Gold...
and I'll let you keep some of the loot so you can repair your ship" I hate to put you jerks outta business!
You idiot!  Eat Lead!Come and get it Pig!
He was nice enough not to kill us.
Another triumph for Porco Rosso!  It's a good thing, we pirate abandoned... together right?  We gotta do somethin' about that stupid Pig!
So you are an American who can help us?
The pirates of the Adriatic, can't have an American protection!
Look at him, his grandma's cousin  was Italian.
And besides Curtis is the only pilot who can beat Porco.
With his snout in the air as always.
Did you know you took twice the reward of Bounty Hunter this year?
And Sir, how does it feel to be the top Bounty Hunter of the Adriatic?
What do you think you doing?
Shutup and listen to the song!
I just might have to take her back home with me.
I bet she can make it big in America.
Although she'll have to stop singing in front of each everytime!
I don't mind saying she made me bit of a celebrity in the racing world.
So you are the one who beat the Italians in the Schneider Cup?
But what I'm best at is Aerial combat.
These pirates tell me that you got a pretty good reputation in the skies.
I'd be careful if you're planning on  making a deal with that Pirate Gangs.
Not only are they lying cheapstakes, not a single one of them knows how to bathe.
We heard that you stupid pig.
While you handsome pirate bosses are...
in one table, you are not here  to cause problems are you?
You know my rule,you eat in my restaraunt..not fight.
We would never fight within 50 miles from your place.
We're even getting along with the pig.
Porco, tell me about your rescue?
Next time just the two of us.
So what do you think about the American flyboy?
As soon as he saw me, he asked me to marry him!
So I told him of the three pilots I've married.
The first died in the war,second died in  the Atlantic, last one he died in Asia.
I got the call last night.They found  his remains in some remote part of Bengal.
I've been waiting to hear something for 3 years...
but now I can't even cry.
Maybe I've run out of tears.
Marco I wanna thank you for keeping an eye on me.
And my restaraunt all these years.
I can't tell you how much your friendship means to me.
Well you know, its a great place...
except from that ugly photograph you keep hanging in the wall up there.
I can't  believe you scribbled over your face!
That's the only picture left of you as a human.
How you ever going to break that stupid curse on you,Marco?
I wish I could make money way you do!
That the last you owe on the seaplane.
Let's see..How about buying some patriotic  bonds to help serve our nation?
Looks like our irons are in for change in government.
If so you Bounty Hunters will soon be outlaws.
Laws don't mean anything to a pig.
Won't mean much to us weapons dealer either.
You  sure you want the usual?  We got the new armor piercing that explode on contact!
So whats the difference between fighting a war and bounty hunting?
If you make money from war, you are scud...
but if you can't make money from bounty hunting you are an idiot!
How in the whole world could we be in debt.This is ridiculous!
We didn't take quite enough money to cover our repairs!
I can't believe we have to work with these losers!
It's the stupid pig's fault boss!
Those Mamma Aiutos guy can't even afford paint?
Its embarassing to be seen with them.
Alright I guess we're all here.
Sighted target: The Queen of the  Mediterranean at 10 'o' Clock.
That's why we doing this as a group.
We share the cost of repairs, if one of us gets hit.
Everyones responsible  for his own expenses.
We are now being attacked by seapirates.
The Queen of the Mediterranean coastline has anticipated this possibility.
And equipped our ship with  two top of the lines pilots!
Now launching from the main desk, Lane#1 The Black Stallion, Sinor Valleta.
And from Lane#2 The Wolf of the Tiber, captain Visconti.
I didn't know they had security.
I've to win this thing myself!
Guess I'll have to take this  baby to Milan for repairs.
With the help of American Donald Curtiss,airpirates shotdown Queen of the Mediterrean 2 security planes   after stealing all the valuables from the  ship,the pirates left the following message..
we're coming for you Porco Rosso!
You really expect me to wait here?
I'm off to Milan Lucious feet, soft bed, beautiful women.
Just tour onto Milan I don't like this weather.
I better duck below the clouds.
If you run away, I'll tell everyone you are chicken!
I need some evidence or no one will believe me.
I might just take it back to Texas as a gift for mom.
There's a phone call for you.
He's on the phone right now.
You can take it at the front desk.
I was just about go search for you in my boat.
A tugboat gave me a lift.
On an island for two days.
Though not sexy as that American flagway.
I'm sure he'll be stopping by your place.
So tell him we'll meet again!
Anyway, I'm in Milan to fix my plane.
The Italians have a warrant out for your arrest, remember?
Don't care how great your mechanic is over there.
You get back home you hear me?
Dont want to yell at you Marco.
If you keep acting so pigheaded,you gonna endup dead Cant go to another pilot's funeral.
Is Porco Rosso dead or alive?
Hey Porco, I thought you would come here tonight.
She really took a beating this time.
Looks like you are missing half of the plane.
Wouldn't it be easier to build a new one?
Lookout, I'm gonna back her in.
So tell me Piccolo, where did you find the girl?
Not many workers around who can do a job like that these days.
Are you sure that girl is your granddaughter, Piccolo?
Fio, you alright getting the plane off the rig?
I gotta outfly an American named Curtiss and my business is in the toilet.
This would give me some extra kick.
Don't ask how I got it.
All I can say is that it came from an Italian sea plane that lost the Schneider Cup to Curtiss in 1927.
But it wasn't the engine's fault.
I'll tune this up, just right.
But don't tune it up too delicately.I'm not flying this thing in a race, you know.
You are talking to the God of engine-work here.
You plan on taking all of my money?
These days money's barely worth the paper it's printed on.
Give me the money you got in your pocket.
Meals included, I won't charge you much.
So Piccolo, haven't seen your sons  around.
They took off to find work.
Then whose  gonna design my plane?
Can't be such a pig.She's a talented  engineer.
I'm  taking my worth money somewhere else.
Are you leaving because I'm a woman?
Or is it because I'm too young?
But tell me, what's you think takes a pilot to be great?
Hmm I just knew you weren't gonna say experience.
Grandpa said you flew solo in the first week and you were a great pilot.
Hmm yeah that was 1910 when I was 17.
That's the same age I am!
I can't help being a woman, but I gurantee you I have talent.
If I don't do a good job, you don't have to pay.
She's my grand daughter, she'll do fine.
Now with me, I was fixing engines at the age of 12.
Why don't you sleep on it.
Left you a clean towel in the bathroom.  Good night!
But since you're a good friend, I've decided to loan you the rest.
Here's a rough draft of the design.
I tweaked the wing section that should make the plane fly atleast five knots faster.
Look I dug up the original blueprints.
I've never seen anything like it.
Then they decided was too dangerous...
I found it covered and dusted in a warehouse 00:32:55,932 --> 00:32:59,527 340   With the wings like that I'm really surprised that you can get it off the water.
Takeoffs and landings can be a little bit tricky.
But get it up to speed, she handles like a dream.
Why don't you try and increase the angle of incidence by half a degree on the wing.
So you're giving me the job?
Alright you got the job but on one condition,Fiona...
No more staying up all night or your work will start getting sloppy.
Also its truly bad for your complexion.
To be honest, I couldn't sleep last night because...
I was afraid you wouldn't give me the job.
I should sleep fine tonight I'll go make some coffee and I'll get back to work.This is so exciting!
I can't wait to start building!
Don't tell me she plans on building the whole plane by herself!
This is Ivana, my other niece her four daughters, Sophia, Laura, Constance and Valentina.
My sons' wives Maria, Tina, Anna, and the trio...showtime!
Porkalino!  Are you girls really still alive?
We thought we get in on the action.
You are not here to build my plane, are you?
Yeah, we need to get some poker money.
So this is the crew, huh?
Don't you have any man relatives?
They had to look elsewhere for work.
You'll see, they're very hard workers.
Yeah we're not baking a cake here!
Heavenly father, we give you thanks for putting bread on our table...
and for giving us work when we were at the brink of bankruptcy Please forgive us for building a fighter plane with the help of women.
Amen Please eat and work on making that cake.
You gonna whip pants off curtiss with this.
I think this might be bad for your shed, Piccolo.
Wait till we turn it up to full speed.
Hmm, so you want to add a trim tab?
Hmm I dunno, this is going to cost a lot of money.
It's a great idea but we already gone way over budget.
Would you stop looking at me like that, Fio.
I've already talked to the manufacturers.  I'll can get the orders filled right away!
I give you three months to pay the bill.
Maybe I should just become an air pirate.
Just looking at her makes me tired.
What you doing back in Italy?
I make a loot come and go, as I please.
The secret police already know you are in the country.
I gave em the slip You gotta get outta Italy now.
I've seen your arrest warrant deserting the Italian Air force, entering the country illegally, being a blatantly unpatriotic pig This is no time to laugh, Marco!
They got it in for you, they want to confiscate your plane.
Marco why don't you come back to the Air Force?
I got influence now I can work something out.
But I rather be a pig than a Fascist.
Then you better keep your plane off the skies.
The only way the Italians will let you fly is if you fly for our country.
You really are a pig, aren't you?
You realise if they can a pig, they won't give you a fair trial.
Give my regards to the guys.
Alright I'll try to lookout for you.
But I can only do so much.
I borrowed this truck so we can take the seaplane to the lake..
We're ready to give it a test flight.
I'm gettin' out of here today.
I refuse to give you the plane without testing it.
Plus it will take atleast a day to take the plane apart and transport it to the lake.
I want you to take a good look behind this van.
Because they like my pretty red plane.
Problem is they don't like me flying it.
Hey, are you a spy or something?
That's the last thing I ever do kid.
But you were a hero during the war, right?
Well this is really strange if you haven't done anything wrong!
How about we try another direction?
Looks like you done this kind of thing before.
Everytime I go to Milan kiddo.
The plane's ready than you were.
Two secret police are hiding out back and three in the front.
I will Fio, what do you think you doing?
Just give me about five seconds.
You are crazy if you think I'm letting you fly along with me.
The secret police will hear you.
There's a warrant out for my arrest, you realize?
This is not a joyride sweetheart,so if you...
It's a bit of a tight fit but it should do.
Fio this is way too dangerous!
I'll be taking it from the canal out back I don't even know if I can get her off the water!
That's why you need to have the engineer with you.
So that I can make adjustments to the plane Don't you get it?
I'll have bullets flying over my head!
I'm responsible for this plane and I wanna do my first job right!
I'm a known womanizer, I live on a deserted island in a small tent.
I'll give you a good deal on the salary.
And I know she will come handy.
Besides I want you back in business, so that I can get paid.
And I'll install this so you two can chit chat.
So you are okay with turning her into an outlaw?
Ehmm..Hmm I'm going along as your hostage.
See that way all my relatives can tell the police that they had no choice but to help you!  So please Porco, let me come.
You better take out one of the machine guns.
Theres not enough space even with your tiny butt.
And you know my butt is bigger than it looks.
I'll have to get out in 2 secs.
If we hang around here much longer, you and the old ladies might come.
And that will cost you a lotta mullah!
Grandma get out of the way!
Hey Fio, you bring back souvenirs.
It's crazy, just like you, Fio.
Its even harder than handle before!
Stop the plane.I'll make some adjustments.
I'll get her up in the air somehow.
It's the crate on your right.
This is such an incredible view!
Its someone from the Italian Air force.
Looks like my old buddy Ferrarin is here.
He says the Air force has a trap for us up ahead.
Knows show how we can get outta here!
If we fly low all the way home, we should stay outta their range.
Thank you very much, my friend!
He said "Cute girl, when did you start babysitting"?
A solitary rose blooms in the secret garden.
That's my favorite line from a screenplay I wrote.
Mr.Curtiss, why are you trespassing in my garden.
I've something special to show you.
“Dear Mr.Curtiss, In regards to the screenplay you sent us...” "We would love to produce it and we would consider you for the lead" The script's title is the Rose of the Adriatic.
Gina, come to Hollywood with me.
I'm already a big celebrity as a pilot!
Soon I'll be a Hollywood star.
Don't you wanna be the First Lady?
I find your humility very charming.
I've a long standing bet coming here!
I bet myself that if a certain man comes to visit me when...
I'm out here in my garden,that the two of us will fall in love.
But that fool only comes to my restaurant at night.
He never stops and shows his face in the daylight.
You chose that stupid pig over me?
Love is a little bit more complicated here than it is in America.
Falling in love, happens to you all the time So have fun in Hollywood, little boy.
You made me bump my head.
I'm just saying hi to a friend.
She was the Lady in the white dress, wasn't she?
that all seaplane pilots of the Adriatic fall madly in love with Gina.
So is Gina really your friend?
Or are you in love with her too?
Turn around, quit yapping and get your butt in your seat.
What's a girl doing up Porco's plane?
He's having a serious conversation with my dad.
Both the new government and the old royalist...
have started striking deals with seaplane pirates.
You are not gonna make a penny hunting pirates these days, Porco.
Well sounds like you are out of a job Porco!
You should join up with one of the two factions.
They pay good money for skills like yours.
Specially after Curtiss goes back to America.
You're the ones who should be going to America.
Farewell to the freedome in Adriatic and to days in god abandon.
The price of gas here is ridiculous.
He's charging us 3 times what we pay in Italy.
Here in the Adriatic Islands, we don't dilute our gas like Italians do.
Can you please explain that to her, Porco?
Then plant your butt that looks bigger than it looks back in the cubby hall.
We're taking off with my hat out.
The gas money is going on your bill anyway!
So when do we fight Curtiss?
No need to now.  I'm outta a job, no ones hiring bounty hunters these days!
You can't let Curtiss run around acting like he shot you down .
It's good to stretch my legs.
Looks like my hideout isn't so hidden anyway.
Half the world population is women.
Hey Fio is no ordinary girl!
She's a first class seaplane engineer.
She redesigned my plane and now it flies better than ever.
She's young, but she's a genius!
I never lie about my seaplane, kid.
She came along just to make sure I pay my bill.
Hey what do you say, we smash his stupid red plane to bits.
And leave him here to rot and dead?
You destroy a work of art?
It happens to be a one of a kind Savoy-S21   We realize it's a nice plane...
And you call yourselves seaplane pilots?
My grandpa has been telling me stories of seaplane pirates ever since I was born.
He says seaplane pirates are the most honorable and trustworthy fighters in the world!.
Everytime they fly both the ocean and the sky purify their hearts.
So they're braver than any pilot in the sky...
and they are mightier than any sailor in the sea!.
Thank you, you make me proud to be a seaplane pirate.
And you should be, I can tell it's not about money or revenge.
Now that girl is something else.
Ok Ms.Fio, we respect you so we'll not destroy the plane that you made!
But we still hate that stinkin' pig's gut and we want payback.
What are you morons talking about?
You can't gangup on a fellow sea plane pilot!
You ought to be completely ashamed of yourselves!
A real seaplane pirate would never fight in a pack like bunch of cowards!
Look at Porco, he just came back so that we could have a re-match with Curtiss.
And defend his reputation like a real sea pirate should.
So if you wanna fight Porco honorably then you fight him in the sky!
but my plane has engine trouble.
She did make some good points.
We should pick someone who can fight Porco.
I think we should talk to Curtiss.
Asking him to fight the pig again?
The contract with him has already expired!
I knew you get into trouble without me!
Look at the mess you got me into now.
So do you want me to challenge for a rematch do you, pig?
Why should I give it to ya?
I won once already and my contract with these boys is expired.
Tell you what, if I win will you marry me darlin'?
But if Porco beats you, then you ought to pay the debt he owes me.
Ms.Fio are you quite ceratin you wanna do this?
You should ask him not me.
Are you gonna fight or not?
I'll gladly fight for the woman that I love!
The fight will take place first thing tomorrow morning!.
Since Fio is doing such an honorable thing, my gang will host!
Hey we like to host too!
Don't forget to show up, pig!
Shut up, just go home already!
What on Earth possessed you, to make that deal?
Well I'm sorry, I guess I shouldn't have been ameaned.
I'm just a stupid little girl!
I should thank you for saving my life back there!
You really put yourself on the line.
It looks like we are into this thing together now.
I hate that word, but somehow when you say it doesn't sound so bad..
My heart's pounding like crazy I guess I was really scared .
I just didn't know you would fight for me Porco!
I should have padded those bills!
Curtiss would have paid a lot more!
Why did you turn into a pig?
All middle aged men are pigs!
You know I've heard a lot about Capt.Marco Rossolini.
My father was in his fighter unit.
He told me that Marco once landed a seaplane in raging sea...  to save the life of an enemy pilot.
What if I kiss you Porco?
Yeah you heard the fairy tale where the girl kisses the frog and turns him back to a handsome prince?
You gotta save it for somebody special.
Seeing you makes me wish I shouldn't have given up being human.
First tell me a story, then I'll goto sleep.
It was the last summer of the great war...
We were flying over the Adriatic, on a routine survellience patrol heading to Istria.
My good buddy Berlini was right beside me.
He had just gotten married to Gina from the Hotel Adriana.
And I was his best man.
But the war called so he had to go back to battle right after the ceremony.
Suddenly we were in the middle of the worst dogfight in my life.
Friends and enemies were falling around me like flies.
I had 3 planes trying to chase me down.
And all I thought about was myself.
Soon I realised I was the only one left from my unit.
But the enemy never let up.
I feel my guts out trying to get away.
My hands and feet went numb.
I could feel myself starting to blackout.
I was sure I was gonna die then suddenly everything around me turned white.
Yeah, it was the strangest thing I ever seen.
A light that was so pure, I figured I must be in heaven.
Then I realized that I had flown into a cloud.
I couldn't hold the stick to fly my plane.
But the plane just kept on flying.
then I saw this strange white band high above me.
Berlini, I thought you were dead!
Where do you think you are going?
When I came to, I was skimming just above the sea, all alone.
God was telling you, it wasn't your time yet.
Seems to me, he was telling me maybe I was a pig and I deserved to be all alone.
The good ones are the ones who died.
Or maybe I'm dead, life as a pig.
It's the same thing as hell.
That stupid kid, he sold me rusted cartridges.
I think you are a great human being, Porco.
They'll turn this into a big party Are all of these people air pirates?
No they are trash all over the Mediterranean.
Yeah you might have a handful of few respectful people but I doubt it.
Not only will I get a wife but also will be getting more famous!
This is a final bouter between Porco Rosso and Donald Curtiss.
So if one of you fights dirty, you'll be disrespected by seaplane pilots for eternity !
The next person I hear whining is dead meat!
This fight will decides the fate of Ms.Fio...
who you all love and respect!
If you do clap your hands, clap now!
We're following official procedures Now both you place your bets on these chairs!
If both sides are satisfied, you should shake hands or something like that!
I like to keep my hands clean.
Let's just get on with it.
We'll go to the church as soon as this is over!
Accordin' to ma sweet mama it isn't love that counts! .
Fio, can we take a picture with you?
Three mins to Curtiss in favor!
We should get them to do this every month!
It looks like its gonna be a one sided fight!
He'll be eating bullets if he climbs up now.
It will be harder for Curtiss to hit him if is closer to the water.
You are trying to make me waste my bullets, aren't you?
The loop is what made Porco the Ace of the Adriatic!
I think I know what's going on here.
Look, there he's in perfect position!
If the pig shoots now, he'll kill Curtiss.
I bet he plans to tire Curtiss out and shoot his engine up instead.
I bet your gun is jammed!
So you wanna play games with me?
Curtiss pulled away from the pig!
The pig's leaving a vapor trail!
I haver never seen a dogfight like this in my life!
She's in her room with the door shut.
I really don't wanna miss this fight!
Gina, Italians know about the fighting.
Get the pig out of there!
I hope I'm not too late!
I cant believe that can keep this up.
Go on, Porco hang in there!
I'm not handing Fio over to a jerk like you!
He's got Curtiss's edge in sight!
You used up all your ammo, you idiot!
And no sucking gun and thanks to Fio's big butt!
I refuse to end this fight with a draw!
There's no way you can hit me with that.
You think you can hit me from there?
You don't even know anything about girls!
The bets can't run off, Fio.
I go where the money goes!
Now we got a boxing match.
Can't you fly this plane any faster?
Sorry maam, but I'm afraid the engine will overheat.
Did you see that left hook I threw?
I'm gonna finish you off in the next round.
This time I'm send you to dreamland Curtiss.
You're the one who is a womanizer!
You fall in love with every woman you meet!
Your the one hoggin' in all the girls...
Don't say Gina like you know her!
Gina says she's been waitin' for ya!
For years now, she's been wanting to meet her in that stupid garden of hers...
The bell sounded the final countdown!
There they are!The Air Force hasn't arrived yet.
End of round 6 Round 7  Gina does not want me, liar.
Why would I make that up?
1..2..3 Who ever gets up first, wins!
I don't wanna see breaking anymore hearts!
The Italian Air Force is on its way here.
So anyone in trouble with the Italian authority better move on out.
And I want to say thanks to you too, Mr.
Next time I'll propose you formally and skip the bet.
But I already know my answer.
You said we are in on this together.
Gina, take her to her respectable society please.
Here come the Italian Air Force.
I'm gonna draw them from the others.
Cmon, let me see Porco flew rings around Italian Air force and they never caught up with him again.
I stayed with Gina for a while and we became good friends.
But soon I decided, it was time to go back to Milan.
Through the years there have been a few wars and a...
good deal of turmoil, but my friendship with Gina has remained strong.
I am now President of the Piccolo Co., and we are busy designing all sorts of...
radical new planes but I take time out every summer to visit the Hotel  Adriana.
The old pirate gang still hang out at Gina's Bar.
Mr.Curtiss does write to me sometimes, although he's yet to become...
the President of the United States.  And he still fondly remembers the summer in the Adriatic.
And as for how Gina's bet turned out... well that's our secret!

Songs Performed by Tokiko Kato VOICES PORCO ROSSO Shuichiro Moriyama MADAME GINA Tokiko Kato MASTER PICCOLO Sanshi Katsura MAMMA AIUTO BOSS Tsunehiko Kamijo Executive Producers Yasuyoshi Tokuma Matsuo Toshimitsu and Yoshio Sasaki Original Story and Screenplay by Hayao Miyazaki Music by Joe Hisaishi English Translation by Stephen Alpert, Haruyo Moriyoshi Jim Hubbert and Ian MacDougall A Studio Ghibli Film Producer Toshio Suzuki Directed by Hayao Miyazaki The End
